                        <br /><br />
                        What differentiates me is the intersection of soft skills and technical execution. I understand urgency without panic. I value collaboration over isolation. I see technical problems not as disruptions, but as systems revealing weaknesses that can be improved. Continuous refinement—of processes, documentation, and response strategy—is central to how I work.
                        <br /><br />
                        My journey from the intensity of professional kitchens to enterprise technical environments reflects adaptability, resilience, and growth. I bring composure under pressure, disciplined troubleshooting, and a strong service mindset to every challenge. That combination enables me to deliver consistent, reliable support in environments where stability matters most.
